AT.name: Citadale - The Legends Trilogy
AT.description: Citadale - The Legends Trilogy includes all three chapters of Citadale. The story is continued to tell the story of Sonja Dorleac on her quest. Many levels to conquer, many hidden gems to find. If you liked the original Citadale, you'll love the trilogy!
